title: Exolaunch overtakes 300 satellites deployed in orbit with SpaceX Transporter-8 rideshare mission
summary: Exolaunch successfully deployed 32 satellites on SpaceX’s Transporter-8 mission, including four satellites for ICEYE, as part of its mission management and integration services. The launch marks a milestone for Exolaunch, bringing its total deployed satellites to over 300.
why_it_matters: The article highlights Exolaunch’s growing role as a mission management and integration services provider in the NewSpace sector, but it does not describe a concrete business deal involving ICEYE or other companies beyond satellite deployment services.

entities.name: Exolaunch
entities.role: Mission management and integration services provider
